# Assets & Build

- Always enqueue via `wp_enqueue_script()` / `wp_enqueue_style()` with proper deps and versioning.
- Load assets conditionally only where needed; avoid global bloat.
- Respect script localization via `wp_localize_script()`/`wp_add_inline_script()` for config.
